    "description": "藉由大量的醫學時事帶領學生到一個有趣的醫學新知英文，學生能學到專業的領域用語並能以英文談論專業用詞、流利的對話，甚至解決問題。課程包含了醫學新知、養生英文及長照護理英文用語<br>Using a journal of medicine to bring the student into a fun environment to learn more about medial knowledge.<br>Student can learn more about this professional field and have a conversation with others using the phrase or term from this field or even solve problems with it.<br><br><br><br><br><br>",
