    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "1.培養學生專業的醫學養生英語<br>2.國內外長照英語使用專有名詞<br>3.專業醫學用字、現代人文明病<br>4.養生之道、運動、重量訓練<br>5.讓學生會說，並聽得懂醫院常用的專業英文<br>",
        "en": "The course includes knowledge from medicine, health, and Long –term care.<br>1.The student could learn professional knowledge of medicine and health.<br>2.Learn the terms in Long-term care.<br>3.Medical terms, Modern Civilized Illness.<br>4.The way of health, Exercise[workout], Weight Training<br>5.Teach the student to listen and speak the terms often used in hospital.<br><br>"
